Title
Text
Join Our Music Loving Community
Rhythm Foundation has been a driving force behind Miami’s evolution into a global music and cultural destination for 35+ years. We are a cultural non-profit, and our work depends on your tax-deductible support. As the managers of the iconic Miami Beach Bandshell, we present 140+ events each year, including free community programs and high-quality performances across genres. Signature events like the North Beach Social, Bandshell Laboratories, Miami Beach Youth Music Festival, Global Sound Series and Arts in the Parks bring together local and international artists.
